    <!-- Service Definitions -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-12 font-heading text-center">
          Insurance Service Definitions
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="service-definition bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Workers' Compensation Insurance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Workers' compensation insurance provides medical benefits and wage replacement to employees who are injured or become ill as a result of their job. Most states require businesses with employees to carry workers' compensation coverage. PCFG specializes in workers' comp for high-risk industries including construction, manufacturing, transportation, and healthcare, offering competitive rates and claims management support. Key benefits include medical expense coverage, lost wage replacement, disability benefits, return-to-work programs, and legal protection for employers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-definition bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">General Liability Insurance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              General liability insurance protects businesses against third-party claims for bodily injury, property damage, personal injury, and advertising injury. It covers legal defense costs, settlements, and judgments if your business is sued. Coverage includes bodily injury claims, property damage, personal and advertising injury, products liability, completed operations, and legal defense costs. The average general liability claim exceeds $15,000, making this essential coverage for all businesses regardless of size or industry.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-definition bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Commercial Auto Insurance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Commercial auto insurance covers vehicles used for business purposes, including company cars, delivery trucks, service vans, heavy equipment, and trailers. It provides liability coverage, physical damage protection, cargo insurance, medical payments, uninsured motorist coverage, and rental reimbursement. PCFG Insurance offers coverage for single vehicles to large commercial fleets across their 15-state service area.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-definition bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Business Owner's Policy (BOP)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              A Business Owner's Policy combines general liability and commercial property insurance into one convenient, cost-effective package. It typically includes business interruption coverage, equipment breakdown protection, and crime coverage options. BOPs are ideal for small to medium-sized businesses such as retail stores, restaurants, professional offices, small manufacturers, service businesses, and contractors.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-definition bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Cyber Liability Insurance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Cyber liability insurance protects businesses from losses resulting from data breaches, cyber attacks, ransomware, and other technology-related incidents. Coverage typically includes notification costs, credit monitoring for affected customers, legal fees, regulatory fines, and business interruption losses. This coverage is essential for any business that handles customer data, processes payments, or relies on digital systems.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-definition bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Employee Benefits</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              PCFG Insurance offers comprehensive employee benefits including group health insurance, dental and vision coverage, life insurance, disability insurance, and retirement plans. They also specialize in ICHRA (Individual Coverage Health Reimbursement Arrangements), which allow employers to reimburse employees tax-free for individual health insurance premiums. These benefits help businesses attract and retain top talent.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How To Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-12 font-heading text-center">
          How to Get Business Insurance from PCFG
        </h2>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-primary-200"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="absolute left-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10">1</div>
              <div class="ml-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Contact PCFG Insurance</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Call <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="text-primary-600 font-semibold">(877) 717-7234</a> or visit pcfginsurance.com to request a quote. You can also fill out the online commercial quote form.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="absolute left-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10">2</div>
              <div class="ml-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Provide Business Information</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Share details about your business including industry type, number of employees, annual revenue, location, and current insurance coverage if applicable.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="absolute left-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10">3</div>
              <div class="ml-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Review Coverage Options</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">A PCFG insurance specialist will analyze your needs and recommend appropriate coverage options including workers' compensation, general liability, commercial auto, or a Business Owner's Policy.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="absolute left-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10">4</div>
              <div class="ml-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Receive and Compare Quotes</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">PCFG works with multiple insurance carriers to provide competitive quotes. Review coverage limits, deductibles, and pricing from different providers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="absolute left-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl z-10">5</div>
              <div class="ml-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Select and Purchase Coverage</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Choose the policy that best fits your business needs and budget. PCFG handles all paperwork and can often provide same-day coverage.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
